Package Controller

Class MainMenu

java.lang.Object
Controller.MainMenu
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainMenu extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The MainMenu controller class which acts as the main page for the application. Allows users to view, Add, Modify, and Delete Appointments and Customers, redirects to the Reports screen and Exit the application.
